import React from 'react'; import '../Confirmation.css'; function BookingConfirmed({ bookingDetails }) { const { name = "N/A", email = "N/A", phone = "N/A", address = "N/A", postalCode = "N/A", bookingDate, timeFrom = "N/A", timeTo = "N/A", selectedService = "N/A", priceBeforeRut = 0, totalArea = 0, rutDiscount = false, } = bookingDetails || {}; // Apply discount if Rutavdrag is selected const discount = rutDiscount ? 50 : 0; // Assuming discount of 50% if Rutavdrag is applied const discountAmount = priceBeforeRut * (discount / 100); const finalAmount = priceBeforeRut - discountAmount; // Format date for display const formattedDate = bookingDate ? new Date(bookingDate).toLocaleDateString('en-GB', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric', }) : 'No Date'; return (

Bekräfta Bokning

Kontrollera att din bokning stämmer, sen klick Bekräfta!

Namn: {name}
E-post: {email}
Phonenummer: {phone}
Adress: {address}
Postnummer: {postalCode}
Datum: {formattedDate}
Service tillgänglig: {timeFrom} - {timeTo}
Service Namn: {selectedService}
Service Pris (innan Rut): SEK {priceBeforeRut}
Total yta (sqm): {totalArea} m²
Rabatt: {discount}%
Totalt belopp: SEK {finalAmount.toFixed(2)}
); } export default BookingConfirmed;
